<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink306">
<l>velpōrk kuriciṉī viyaṉcura ṉiṟappiṟ</l>
<l>palkā ḻalku lavvari vāṭak</l>
<l>kuḻaliṉu miṉaikuvaḷ peritē</l>
<l>viḻavoli kūntaṉ māa yōḷē</l>
      </lg>
<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>O king victorious in battles! If you leave for the vast desert,</l>
<l>the dark[-skinned] girl, whose tresses are decorated for the festival,</l>
<l>will wail louder than a flute, </l>
<l>as pretty outline of her hips, [adorned] with many gems, looses beauty.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
